description: Redevelopment of site involving the extension of the existing building to a 6 storey plus basement building and a part 6 and part 7 storey plus basement building to provide 5778sqm of Class B1/B2 floorspace and 98 residential units (7919sqm) comprising 45 x 1 bed and 53 x 2 bed units together with 35 basement car parking spaces.
